title: Mischa Bredewold sprints to headline victory at GP Plouay
content:
Dutchwoman wins scrappy sprint in Classic Lorient Agglomération-Trophée Ceratizit after she crashed into a ditch earlier in the race.

Read the full article at Mischa Bredewold sprints to headline victory at GP Plouay on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
